{"tid":775191,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報怒批蘋果：iphone利潤這麼高，只分給中國企業1.8%！","createTime":"2018-08-11T03:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T21:27:05.000Z","uid":9136,"like":436,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"841c445cf329d1d09807fd6b4a88c26bfebaca4e","tid":775191,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"眾所周知，蘋果公司是世界上手機以及科技業的巨頭企業。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">近日，人民日報卻發表一句這樣的評論：蘋果公司長期以來享受中國的廉價勞動力以及強大的供應鏈，蘋果必須將它在中國的利潤分享給中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n人民日報文章還引用了一組數據稱，在蘋果公司供應鏈中，來自中國的企業，只獲得了iphone機型整機利潤的1.8%！</span><br />\n<br />\n也就是說，一台iphone的利潤有100元的話，中國企業只獲得了其中的1.8元。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知道，就在上周，蘋果公司的市值已經突破了萬億，使得蘋果公司為第一個突破萬億的科技公司。<br />\n在蘋果最新的一份財報中顯示，蘋果公司在中國地區的收入為95.5億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nd黨煤真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要人地一間私人企業無條件派錢比你？你邊位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔見東江水年年賺我地幾億 你會回饋番d利潤比香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7268e46a54e287abe0397d87ffacd9a1db744b","tid":775191,"uid":69098,"like":245,"dislike":3,"score":242,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"你咪唔好代工囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216db6dab17bb5ebaa2e3e4ea12c605581b8296b","tid":775191,"uid":60982,"like":167,"dislike":7,"score":160,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"人民日報都睇 你夠痴撚線喇"},{"pid":"e770dee127d7ce557cf2cd4afd247ac45f97a280","tid":775191,"uid":50457,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:25:34.000Z","msg":"投入成本呢？個腦生係屎忽度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33de1bba7994a1dbc55a87853e23dfa906f1f